        "subject": "LU-10707 lnet: backport of lnet fixes for 2.10",
        "message": "LU-10707 lnet: backport of lnet fixes for 2.10\n\nBackport of all the patches needed to resolve several issues:\n\n1) Support for MOFED 4.X versions\n\n2) Using ARM with LU-10157 breaks with current 2.10\n\n3) Resolve LU-10707\n\nThis is for testing.\n\nChange-Id: I42fd5620ab8131cd5fdf4bf0ef15553f6eabe550\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@yahoo.com>\n"
